https://angular.io/guide/setup-local

1. Ceate the application
https://angular.io/cli/new

npm i -g @angular/cli
ng new example-app --skip-git=true --skip-tests=true
ng serve -o

2. Generate module
https://angular.io/cli/generate#module-command
Add an eager module
ng g m modules/common -m app.module
Add a lazy module
ng g m modules/common -m app.module --route common

2. Add route
https://angular.io/guide/lazy-loading-ngmodules
forRoot() and forChild()
https://stackoverflow.com/questions/40498081/routermodule-forrootroutes-vs-routermodule-forchildroutes#:~:text=forRoot%20creates%20a%20module%20that,not%20include%20the%20router%20service.



